    <item>
      <title>马斯克的右翼盟友抓住巴西选举前禁令的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/elon-musk-s-right-wing-allies-seize-on-brazil-x-ban-heading-into-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西对社交媒体平台 X 的禁令可能会给所有者埃隆·马斯克带来经济挫折，但对这位亿万富翁及其右翼盟友来说，这也是一个潜在的政治机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/elon-musk-s-right-wing-allies-seize-on-brazil-x-ban-heading-into-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议者在司法辩论前封锁墨西哥国会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[示威者组成人链，封锁墨西哥众议院，抗议总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的司法改革法案，议员们定于周二对该法案进行辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:48:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国比亚迪暂停墨西哥工厂建设计划直至美国大选结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国最大的电动汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司至少要在美国大选之后才会宣布在墨西哥投资大型工厂，因为美国政策的变化迫使全球企业进入观望模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:14:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列财政部长承诺削减开支以资助战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/israel-finance-minister-commits-to-cutbacks-to-help-fund-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列财政部长概述了明年拖延已久的财政计划，表示将通过削减预算、冻结工资和增加收入来筹集更多的战争开支，而不是扩大赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/israel-finance-minister-commits-to-cutbacks-to-help-fund-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙将任命埃斯克里瓦为央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/spain-to-name-escriva-new-central-bank-governor-expansion-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《Expansion》援引未透露姓名的人士报道称，西班牙将任命现任数字事务部长何塞·路易斯·埃斯克里瓦 (Jose Luis Escriva) 为新任西班牙央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/spain-to-name-escriva-new-central-bank-governor-expansion-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:58:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚央行行长认为该协议将恢复石油供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/libyan-central-banker-sadiq-al-kabir-sees-deal-soon-that-will-restore-oil-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚央行行长表示，利比亚似乎即将达成协议，以解决争端并刺激恢复重要的石油生产。利比亚正处于欧佩克敌对政府之间的权力斗争之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/libyan-central-banker-sadiq-al-kabir-sees-deal-soon-that-will-restore-oil-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:52:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯为有争议的英国冬季燃料补贴削减进行辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uk-s-reeves-defends-controversial-cut-to-winter-fuel-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯为她削减大多数养老金领取者的冬季燃料补贴的有争议的决定进行辩护，称此举有助于恢复英国公共财政秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uk-s-reeves-defends-controversial-cut-to-winter-fuel-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:53:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基再次恳求俄罗斯导弹袭击造成 51 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/zelenskiy-says-41-people-killed-in-russian-strike-on-poltava</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基强调要部署防空系统，此前俄罗斯导弹袭击造成 50 多人死亡，这是自 2022 年 2 月克里姆林宫入侵以来最致命的袭击之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/zelenskiy-says-41-people-killed-in-russian-strike-on-poltava</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称美国钢铁公司应继续由美国所有和经营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯与总统乔·拜登共同宣布，美国钢铁公司应保持国内所有和运营，这是该公司拟出售给日本新日本制铁公司的计划遭遇的最新阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
